===Noun===
'''libertarian'''

# Someone who advocates [[liberty]].
# Someone who opposes [[authority]] and [[hierarchy]].
# Capitalised: A member of a political party or movement that advocates individual rights and a limited government.

===Adjective===
'''libertarian'''

# Of, promoting or practicing [[liberty]].
# Capitalised: Related or belonging to or constituting a political party or movement that identifies itself as promoting liberty.

